<text top="2173" left="1247" width="438" height="46" font="font11" id="p1_t92" reading_order_no="90" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">puting  (Nov.—Dec.  2005),  86-88. </text>
<text top="2212" left="1216" width="964" height="46" font="font11" id="p1_t93" reading_order_no="91" segment_no="9" tag_type="text">2.  Singh,  M.P.  The  Pragmatic  Web:  Preliminary  thoughts.  In  Proceedings </text>
<text top="2248" left="1252" width="928" height="46" font="font11" id="p1_t94" reading_order_no="92" segment_no="9" tag_type="text">of  the  NSF-OntoWeb  Workshop  on  Database  and  Information  Systems </text>
<text top="2289" left="1251" width="811" height="43" font="font12" id="p1_t95" reading_order_no="93" segment_no="9" tag_type="text">Research  for  Semantic  Web  and  Enterprises,  (Apr.  2002),  82-90. </text>
