<text top="2445" left="1216" width="904" height="43" font="font12" id="p1_t97" reading_order_no="95" segment_no="10" tag_type="text">information  systems  at  the  University  of  Hohenheim,  Germany. </text>
<text top="2487" left="1216" width="906" height="42" font="font8" id="p1_t98" reading_order_no="96" segment_no="11" tag_type="text">ALDO  DE  Moor  (ademoor@vub.ac.be)  is  a  senior  researcher  at </text>
<text top="2530" left="1215" width="670" height="41" font="font14" id="p1_t99" reading_order_no="97" segment_no="11" tag_type="text">VUB  STARLab,  Universiteit  Brussel,  Belgium. </text>
